      "updated": 1777408150721,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "List of Items in Profile\n1. Cover Image\n2. Profile Picture\n3. Display Name\n4. Username(unique for every user)\n5. Bio\n6. Location\n7. Settings\n    - Profile Details\n    - Change Password\n    - Notifications Toggle\n    - Sign Out\n    - Verification\n    - Delete Account\n    - Location\n8. Pronouns\n",
      "fontSize": 92,
