      "updated": 1777406826997,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "List of fields in the form :\n1. Event Title*\n2. City* -> Zone*\n3. Date*\n4. Time\n5. Full Address*\n6. Category*\n7. Event Description*\n6. Images\n7. Ticket Link*\n8. Age Limit*\n\n\nButtons\n1. Submit Form\n2. Upload Image\n3. Calendar in select date\n\nfeilds with * are mandatory",
      "fontSize": 76,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wZFnjKwh5KOuadeaqmhiG",
      "originalText": "List of fields in the form :\n1. Event Title*\n2. City* -> Zone*\n3. Date*\n4. Time\n5. Full Address*\n6. Category*\n7. Event Description*\n6. Images\n7. Ticket Link*\n8. Age Limit*\n\n\nButtons\n1. Submit Form\n2. Upload Image\n3. Calendar in select date\n\nfeilds with * are mandatory",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
